Text: Re Christmas party December thnsf Guz Were still having a party on Saturday night I didnt get the invitations out in a timely fashion so here is your official invitation complete with directions When Saturday night pm or so Where NE Andover St Hillsboro OR How Take to Cornelius Pass Road You will cross back over going the correct direction on Cornelius Pass Road Head straight miles to Quatama look for the Elks Lodge sign take right onto Quatama yards take an immediate left We are in the first condo on your left There are under construction across the street and it will be very hard to miss Call us if you get lost but you should be all good Bring a friend if you want and a beverage of your choice We will have beer vino and some food Hope you can make it and sorry about the delay getting this to you Boyd From To Subject Re Christmas party December th Date Mon Dec My address is NW th Apt Portland OR Get more from the Web FREE MSN Explorer download
